<% layout("layouts/boilerplate")%>
<style>
    /* Reset some default styles */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Global styles */
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  color: #333;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #007bff;
}

/* Main content styles */
main {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 40px 20px;
}

.about-section,
.team-section {
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}

.about-section h2,
.team-section h2 {
  font-size: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.about-content {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 40px;
}

.about-image {
  flex: 0 0 500px;
}

.about-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.about-info {
  flex-grow: 1;
}

.about-info p {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.cta-button {
  display: inline-block;
  background-color: #007bff;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.team-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  grid-gap: 30px;
}

.team-member {
  background-color: #f5f5f5;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  overflow: hidden;
  text-align: center;
}

.team-member img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.team-member h3 {
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

.team-member p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #666;
  margin-top: 5px;
}
</style>
<body>
  <main>
    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>About Quiz Enthusiast</h2>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="about-hero.jpg" alt="Quiz Enthusiast">
        </div>
        <div class="about-info">
          <p>Quiz Enthusiast is the premier destination for quiz takers and creators alike. Our mission is to provide a fun, engaging, and educational platform where people of all interests can test their knowledge, discover new passions, and challenge their friends.</p>
          <p>Since our inception, we've been dedicated to curating an ever-expanding library of high-quality quizzes that cover a wide range of topics, from science and history to sports and entertainment. Whether you're a trivia buff or simply curious to learn more, you'll find something to pique your interest on Quiz Enthusiast.</p>
          <p>Our team of dedicated quiz experts work tirelessly to ensure that each quiz is accurate, well-designed, and truly captivating. We believe that learning should be enjoyable, and that's why we strive to make every quiz experience both informative and entertaining.</p>
          <a href="#" class="cta-button">Create Your Own Quiz</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team-section">
      <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-member">
          <img src="team-member-1.jpg" alt="John Doe">
          <h3>John Doe</h3>
          <p>Co-Founder and CEO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <img src="team-member-2.jpg" alt="Jane Smith">
          <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
          <p>Co-Founder and CTO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <img src="team-member-3.jpg" alt="Michael Johnson">
          <h3>Michael Johnson</h3>
          <p>Head of Content</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <img src="team-member-4.jpg" alt="Sarah Lee">
          <h3>Sarah Lee</h3>
          <p>Lead Designer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>